1
00:00:06,927 --> 00:00:11,364
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

2
00:00:11,432 --> 00:00:14,959
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

3
00:00:15,036 --> 00:00:18,472
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

4
00:00:18,539 --> 00:00:22,134
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh! Just go my way</i>

5
00:00:22,209 --> 00:00:25,474
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

6
00:00:25,546 --> 00:00:27,480
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>

7
00:00:29,283 --> 00:00:32,218
<i>Down a difficult road</i>
<i>filled with endless struggles</i>

8
00:00:32,286 --> 00:00:36,086
<i>Where do you think you are going</i>
<i>following someone else's map?</i>

9
00:00:36,490 --> 00:00:43,328
<i>An insightful crow comes along</i>
<i>to tear up the map</i>

10
00:00:43,564 --> 00:00:50,629
<i>Now open your eyes and</i>
<i>take a look at the truth (Yeah!)</i>

11
00:00:50,938 --> 00:00:57,070
<i>There's nothing to lose,</i>
<i>so let's GO!!!</i>

12
00:00:57,211 --> 00:01:01,477
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

13
00:01:01,549 --> 00:01:05,144
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

14
00:01:05,219 --> 00:01:08,552
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

15
00:01:08,622 --> 00:01:12,251
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh!</i>
<i>Just go my way</i>

16
00:01:12,326 --> 00:01:15,921
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

17
00:01:15,996 --> 00:01:19,488
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best!</i>

18
00:01:19,567 --> 00:01:23,025
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

19
00:01:23,237 --> 00:01:27,333
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!</i>

20
00:01:43,401 --> 00:01:48,100
How is that your answer...
Princess Tsunade?

21
00:01:49,107 --> 00:01:51,701
To think you'd try to kill me...

22
00:01:54,045 --> 00:01:56,980
At any rate,
I have a sincere trust in you, Kabuto.

23
00:01:57,649 --> 00:02:04,020
A trust for your loyalty and your eyes
that spotted Tsunade's attack.

24
00:02:04,522 --> 00:02:07,320
Yes. We're both from
the same medical corps so...

25
00:02:08,093 --> 00:02:09,890
Her Chakra was overflowing
with violent intent.

26
00:02:13,765 --> 00:02:19,499
Tsunade... I was really planning
on resurrecting those two people.

27
00:02:20,772 --> 00:02:25,175
And here I went so far as to promise
not to smash the Leaf Village...

28
00:02:34,819 --> 00:02:35,911
Orochimaru...

29
00:02:37,322 --> 00:02:42,760
I know that your promise of
"not touching the village" was a lie...

30
00:02:45,397 --> 00:02:48,161
Even though I knew that... I...

31
00:02:52,771 --> 00:02:56,366
Just one more time
would've been fine...

32
00:02:57,609 --> 00:03:00,077
Just one more time,
I wanted to see them...

33
00:03:02,180 --> 00:03:05,377
Just one more time...
I wanted to touch them...

34
00:03:07,152 --> 00:03:11,816
Just one more time...
To see those smiling faces...

35
00:03:13,325 --> 00:03:14,223
But...

36
00:03:16,261 --> 00:03:20,357
the moment I felt that
rush in my bones...

37
00:03:20,899 --> 00:03:24,767
that I'd be able to see Nawaki
and Dan shortly...

38
00:03:26,671 --> 00:03:29,834
I realized that I'm a hopeless fool!

39
00:03:34,846 --> 00:03:38,646
Just by remembering those faces...

40
00:03:39,784 --> 00:03:42,378
I become this blinded.

41
00:03:43,788 --> 00:03:44,846
<i>Big sister!</i>

42
00:03:45,890 --> 00:03:46,788
<i>Tsunade...</i>

43
00:03:47,792 --> 00:03:51,751
I loved them...
I truly loved them!

44
00:03:52,197 --> 00:03:55,257
So, I wanted to see them
and hug them in my arms!

45
00:04:03,274 --> 00:04:05,469
But... I couldn't...

46
00:04:07,379 --> 00:04:10,246
<i>I won't lose the bet,</i>
<i>no matter what!</i>

47
00:04:11,282 --> 00:04:16,049
Because of that kid...
I remembered the dreams of the two.

48
00:04:17,555 --> 00:04:19,113
Here I was trying to forget...

49
00:04:20,258 --> 00:04:22,692
<i>This village is grandfather's treasure!</i>

50
00:04:23,094 --> 00:04:24,686
<i>I'm going to protect it!</i>

51
00:04:25,230 --> 00:04:27,664
<i>'Cuz I'm the grandson</i>
<i>of the First Hokage</i>

52
00:04:27,732 --> 00:04:29,962
<i>who built the Village Hidden in Leaves!</i>

53
00:04:30,969 --> 00:04:33,870
<i>I love this village and my comrades...</i>

54
00:04:35,340 --> 00:04:36,739
<i>So I want to protect them.</i>

55
00:04:40,111 --> 00:04:42,079
<i>Right! Someday,</i>
<i>I'll become just like Grandfather.</i>

56
00:04:42,147 --> 00:04:44,411
<i>And the Hokage name will be mine!</i>

57
00:04:45,950 --> 00:04:51,616
<i>Unlike you... I will be the heir to</i>
<i>the Hokage name, no matter what!</i>

58
00:04:52,690 --> 00:04:57,525
<i>Since my little sister died,</i>
<i>that sole thought has sustained me.</i>

59
00:04:58,563 --> 00:05:00,292
<i>So I'll become the Hokage...</i>

60
00:05:01,332 --> 00:05:03,823
<i>An existence that protects everyone...</i>

61
00:05:10,008 --> 00:05:12,806
- <i>Becoming the Hokage is my dream!</i>
- <i>Becoming the Hokage is my dream!</i>

62
00:05:15,713 --> 00:05:18,648
The precious dreams that
they risked their lives for...

63
00:05:18,983 --> 00:05:22,749
Making those dreams come true
was also my desire...

64
00:05:26,491 --> 00:05:30,427
Things that have formed
eventually decay... You said that.

65
00:05:39,838 --> 00:05:40,805
But...

66
00:05:44,142 --> 00:05:47,771
after all, these are feelings
that won't decay...

67
00:05:53,718 --> 00:05:57,085
So our negotiations have broken down...
It can't be helped.

68
00:05:57,755 --> 00:06:01,316
Since it's come to this, I have no choice
but to ask forcibly.

69
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:14,103
<i>Breakdown! The Deal is Off!</i>

70
00:06:27,785 --> 00:06:29,548
Come! Orochimaru!

71
00:06:32,056 --> 00:06:33,023
Come to think of it,

72
00:06:33,091 --> 00:06:36,527
we've never gone at it
even once until now.

73
00:06:40,798 --> 00:06:41,730
That's right!

74
00:06:41,799 --> 00:06:42,993
What're you saying?

75
00:06:43,334 --> 00:06:44,824
I'm the one who has
to go at it with her, right?

76
00:06:45,436 --> 00:06:49,065
Now I'm going to kill
you two worthless punks... here!

77
00:06:51,042 --> 00:06:52,771
Incredible strength as usual...

78
00:06:53,745 --> 00:06:56,145
It'll be over if you're hit once.

79
00:06:56,781 --> 00:06:58,180
I can see that...

80
00:07:01,352 --> 00:07:04,685
It's a bit cramped here
for fighting at a distance.

81
00:07:05,089 --> 00:07:06,317
Are you going to change the location?

82
00:07:07,058 --> 00:07:08,252
That would probably be better...

83
00:07:09,861 --> 00:07:13,558
There was another troublesome person
with the Lady Tsunade's attendant.

84
00:07:15,066 --> 00:07:16,533
That person may come
to her aid.

85
00:07:18,303 --> 00:07:19,235
You're going down!

86
00:07:22,273 --> 00:07:25,174
Who is... the troublesome person?

87
00:07:25,443 --> 00:07:27,604
One of Sannin,
the same as you and Lady Tsunade...

88
00:07:32,450 --> 00:07:33,474
<i>Jiraiya!</i>

89
00:07:41,926 --> 00:07:44,554
<i>I won't let you get away,</i>
<i>no matter what!</i>

90
00:07:50,735 --> 00:07:52,999
Wh-What's this?!

91
00:07:54,272 --> 00:08:00,700
Huh... Princess Tsunade tore it up...
big time.

92
00:08:01,546 --> 00:08:04,913
<i>This means that Lady Tsunade refused...</i>

93
00:08:07,118 --> 00:08:09,450
Where did old Tsunade go?

94
00:08:15,293 --> 00:08:16,817
<i>That belongs to Lady Tsunade...!</i>

95
00:08:20,031 --> 00:08:21,658
Tonton... Which way?

96
00:08:23,835 --> 00:08:24,802
Okay!

97
00:08:43,254 --> 00:08:46,849
It looks like you're quite
out of breath, too... Tsunade.

98
00:08:48,059 --> 00:08:49,356
It's just about time.

99
00:08:51,696 --> 00:08:55,029
I'm not that great at Taijutsu, but...

100
00:09:00,738 --> 00:09:01,705
<i>A Food Pill!</i>

101
00:09:10,415 --> 00:09:11,439
<i>That Sign...!</i>

102
00:09:15,753 --> 00:09:18,017
<i>This kid can also use Medical Ninjutsu...</i>

103
00:09:45,116 --> 00:09:45,980
<i>He got my muscle...!</i>

104
00:09:47,552 --> 00:09:49,019
I severed, ever so slightly,

105
00:09:49,087 --> 00:09:52,113
the bicep muscle of your upper arm
and the rectus muscle of your thigh.

106
00:09:52,857 --> 00:09:55,325
Now you won't be able to release
your incredible strength.

107
00:09:56,194 --> 00:09:59,925
A Chakra scalpel, eh...
Why don't you target the arteries?

108
00:10:01,065 --> 00:10:02,623
Indeed, with this scalpel,

109
00:10:02,700 --> 00:10:07,069
I could cut the muscles and vessels
without external injury.

110
00:10:07,839 --> 00:10:09,238
But as may be expected,

111
00:10:09,307 --> 00:10:12,242
I can't make a long, delicate scalpel
in the middle of battle

112
00:10:12,310 --> 00:10:14,972
that can reach the arteries
and the heart muscle.

113
00:10:15,913 --> 00:10:17,039
But, even so...

114
00:10:17,582 --> 00:10:20,779
there'd be no problem at all
if I target the opponent's neck!

115
00:10:30,094 --> 00:10:33,689
<i>Dang it! My intercostals got hit.</i>
<i>My breathing...</i>

116
00:10:35,333 --> 00:10:38,200
<i>He's no ordinary Medical Ninja.</i>

117
00:10:39,403 --> 00:10:43,066
<i>His Jutsu sense and his edge</i>
<i>exceed even me in my heyday!</i>

118
00:10:45,276 --> 00:10:47,972
It would still be trouble
if you were to die on me.

119
00:10:48,780 --> 00:10:50,077
I won't target your vital spot...

120
00:10:50,882 --> 00:10:53,976
But with this, you can't move anymore...

121
00:11:08,232 --> 00:11:09,392
<i>She's amazing...</i>

122
00:11:10,301 --> 00:11:13,464
<i>Ordinarily, one wouldn't be able</i>
<i>to budge due to difficulty breathing.</i>

123
00:11:15,540 --> 00:11:20,842
<i>It looks like it will be necessary</i>
<i>to rough her up a little more...</i>

124
00:11:23,514 --> 00:11:24,845
<i>but not enough to kill her.</i>

125
00:11:32,824 --> 00:11:34,587
<i>Even though I'm trying to move my hand...</i>

126
00:11:36,227 --> 00:11:38,024
<i>my leg moves?!</i>

127
00:11:39,997 --> 00:11:41,658
<i>D-Don't tell me! This is...</i>

128
00:11:44,268 --> 00:11:45,064
You little!

129
00:11:52,443 --> 00:11:53,740
<i>In my present condition,</i>

130
00:11:53,811 --> 00:11:55,972
<i>this seems to be the extent of my power...</i>

131
00:12:03,087 --> 00:12:04,145
I see...

132
00:12:05,790 --> 00:12:11,023
<i>It's... It's not the muscles...</i>
<i>It's the nerves!</i>

133
00:12:13,197 --> 00:12:17,395
It seems you've realized...
That's right. It's the nerves!

134
00:12:18,736 --> 00:12:20,897
I changed Chakra into electricity...

135
00:12:21,138 --> 00:12:25,074
made an electrical field and
poured electricity into your nerves.

136
00:12:26,744 --> 00:12:29,269
<i>The communication between</i>
<i>the brain and the body</i>

137
00:12:29,380 --> 00:12:32,315
<i>is all done with electric signals...</i>

138
00:12:33,384 --> 00:12:38,879
<i>Tsunade jumbled up all of</i>
<i>the electric signals that are exchanged</i>

139
00:12:39,390 --> 00:12:41,858
<i>at a velocity of 360 kilometers per hour.</i>

140
00:12:44,328 --> 00:12:46,853
<i>Having left battle and yet such power...</i>

141
00:12:46,931 --> 00:12:49,161
<i>So this is the legendary Sannin?</i>

142
00:12:52,970 --> 00:12:55,734
<i>Healing types use too much Chakra...</i>

143
00:12:56,507 --> 00:12:57,633
<i>But in this condition...</i>

144
00:13:04,415 --> 00:13:06,007
<i>If I try to move my right hand...</i>

145
00:13:08,786 --> 00:13:10,219
<i>my left leg moves.</i>

146
00:13:11,722 --> 00:13:13,815
<i>If I try to move my left ankle...</i>

147
00:13:16,127 --> 00:13:17,389
<i>my right shoulder moves.</i>

148
00:13:31,409 --> 00:13:32,376
<i>It's difficult...</i>

149
00:13:33,611 --> 00:13:39,379
<i>But I've already grasped eighty percent</i>
<i>of what moves when I move what.</i>

150
00:13:41,185 --> 00:13:42,880
<i>Don't mess with me...</i>

151
00:13:43,387 --> 00:13:44,684
with this low-level...

152
00:13:47,491 --> 00:13:48,480
Jutsu!

153
00:13:49,093 --> 00:13:51,891
<i>What?! In only a moment,</i>
<i>his body movements...</i>

154
00:13:51,963 --> 00:13:54,022
You're scared of blood, aren't you?!

155
00:13:55,333 --> 00:13:57,358
I'll show you plenty from now!

156
00:14:22,560 --> 00:14:23,492
<i>Jiraiya...?</i>

157
00:14:24,896 --> 00:14:27,456
It's been a long time... Jiraiya.

158
00:14:29,567 --> 00:14:30,727
<i>Orochimaru...</i>

159
00:14:33,304 --> 00:14:36,501
You've got an evil look as usual.

160
00:14:42,881 --> 00:14:43,779
Huh?!

161
00:14:43,848 --> 00:14:45,577
K-Kabuto?

162
00:14:47,385 --> 00:14:48,477
Naruto...

163
00:14:52,657 --> 00:14:54,852
I see... So you know each other?

164
00:14:55,627 --> 00:14:58,425
We took the Chunin Exam together!

165
00:14:59,797 --> 00:15:01,765
Why are you here, Kabuto...?

166
00:15:03,968 --> 00:15:04,696
Get out of the way!

167
00:15:05,036 --> 00:15:05,661
Hey...

168
00:15:07,105 --> 00:15:07,969
I'll take...

169
00:15:08,406 --> 00:15:09,498
these guys!

170
00:15:12,343 --> 00:15:15,369
Just because you've mastered
your body movements...

171
00:15:16,247 --> 00:15:17,942
it doesn't mean...

172
00:15:18,516 --> 00:15:19,983
you can move like normal!

173
00:15:23,221 --> 00:15:24,449
I won't let you get away now!

174
00:15:25,523 --> 00:15:26,455
Too late!

175
00:15:38,836 --> 00:15:41,669
My body movements have
finally returned...

176
00:15:42,941 --> 00:15:43,737
<i>Blood...!</i>

177
00:15:46,811 --> 00:15:51,271
Having two of the legendary Sannin
as opponents is hairy, isn't it...?

178
00:15:52,116 --> 00:15:54,414
So even if it's just one...
I'll stop you!

179
00:15:56,688 --> 00:15:57,620
Lady Tsunade!

180
00:15:59,390 --> 00:16:03,622
Say! Say! What's happening?!

181
00:16:04,095 --> 00:16:06,393
Why's Kabuto fighting
with old Tsunade?!

182
00:16:07,599 --> 00:16:11,091
You're slow, Naruto...

183
00:16:13,137 --> 00:16:15,571
That's why you're no match for Sasuke.

184
00:16:18,776 --> 00:16:21,142
Take a good look at the headband!

185
00:16:22,447 --> 00:16:24,608
He's Orochimaru's subordinate.

186
00:16:25,249 --> 00:16:26,011
Wha?!

187
00:16:27,051 --> 00:16:27,915
That's right...

188
00:16:28,319 --> 00:16:30,844
I was a spy from
the Village Hidden in the Sound.

189
00:16:34,225 --> 00:16:36,659
Wh-What're you saying?

190
00:16:37,362 --> 00:16:39,353
You're lying, right, Kabuto?

191
00:16:41,466 --> 00:16:44,958
During the Chunin Exam
you taught us a lot...

192
00:16:45,036 --> 00:16:46,526
And you also saved us.

193
00:16:46,771 --> 00:16:51,174
Well, I wanted to gather data
on you guys.

194
00:16:52,677 --> 00:16:57,546
Naruto, there's something
I understood by gathering your data.

195
00:17:00,151 --> 00:17:02,176
You have no Ninja ability.

196
00:17:04,555 --> 00:17:06,147
Unlike Sasuke!

197
00:17:18,403 --> 00:17:21,270
<i>It's the first time</i>
<i>I've seen Lady Tsunade like this...</i>

198
00:17:32,850 --> 00:17:35,410
Please don't push it too far alone.

199
00:17:37,855 --> 00:17:40,653
I'm your attendant, so...

200
00:17:42,260 --> 00:17:43,784
<i>Old Lady Tsunade...</i>

201
00:17:46,197 --> 00:17:48,062
Even with a fierce look,

202
00:17:48,433 --> 00:17:51,402
you're just a cute Genin
who's a fish out of water.

203
00:17:53,571 --> 00:17:56,972
Admittedly, I was anticipating
the monster dwelling inside you...

204
00:17:57,408 --> 00:18:00,172
But now,
with the legendary Sannin before me,

205
00:18:00,478 --> 00:18:02,070
you leave something to be desired.

206
00:18:03,648 --> 00:18:08,642
You're just a puny zero.
So if you meddle...

207
00:18:11,489 --> 00:18:12,478
I'll kill you.

208
00:18:14,792 --> 00:18:15,759
You little!

209
00:18:16,327 --> 00:18:17,316
Don't, Naruto!

210
00:18:18,563 --> 00:18:19,894
<i>My body's still...</i>

211
00:18:21,499 --> 00:18:22,431
<i>That hand...</i>

212
00:18:23,034 --> 00:18:25,298
<i>He shouldn't be able to use</i>
<i>that right hand anymore.</i>

213
00:18:27,271 --> 00:18:28,738
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

214
00:18:29,674 --> 00:18:31,835
<i>I'll attack at once with four...</i>

215
00:18:31,909 --> 00:18:35,003
<i>and break him from the right side</i>
<i>where he can't defend!</i>

216
00:18:39,951 --> 00:18:40,713
You little!

217
00:18:41,319 --> 00:18:41,944
Okay!

218
00:18:44,422 --> 00:18:45,218
<i>What?</i>

219
00:18:47,091 --> 00:18:47,853
<i>Blood?</i>

220
00:19:04,575 --> 00:19:05,371
<i>Poison Needles!</i>

221
00:19:06,277 --> 00:19:08,575
<i>My neural reflexes still haven't</i>
<i>completely returned!</i>

222
00:19:09,614 --> 00:19:10,808
<i>I can't dodge completely!</i>

223
00:19:14,919 --> 00:19:16,045
<i>With the headband...!</i>

224
00:19:17,088 --> 00:19:19,079
<i>Good job, acting so quickly...</i>

225
00:19:24,195 --> 00:19:25,753
Thanks, Shizune!

226
00:19:33,638 --> 00:19:34,468
<i>That's...</i>

227
00:19:38,176 --> 00:19:39,370
A Plasma Pill!

228
00:19:40,311 --> 00:19:41,437
A Plasma Pill?

229
00:19:46,284 --> 00:19:50,015
So he's trying to replenish
lost blood, huh...

230
00:19:50,354 --> 00:19:53,619
That kid is a Medical Ninja same as me...

231
00:19:54,559 --> 00:19:57,858
The blood is gushing out nicely,
eh, Kabuto?

232
00:19:58,596 --> 00:19:59,563
Lord Orochimaru...

233
00:20:00,498 --> 00:20:02,796
Please take off the bandage
on your left arm.

234
00:20:17,281 --> 00:20:19,772
That man is Orochimaru...

235
00:20:20,151 --> 00:20:22,915
At last, the real thing appears...

236
00:20:25,056 --> 00:20:26,023
Shizune!

237
00:20:26,624 --> 00:20:27,682
Y-Yes!

238
00:20:28,125 --> 00:20:30,889
You take care of...
that guy with the glasses!

239
00:20:36,300 --> 00:20:38,768
I'll take care of Orochimaru!

240
00:21:05,764 --> 00:21:10,463
<i>I believe your promise,</i>
<i>its a true heart give me courage</i>

241
00:21:10,535 --> 00:21:14,869
<i>Always I feel it</i>
<i>the precious time with you</i>

242
00:21:15,474 --> 00:21:19,001
<i>On your still shoulder</i>

243
00:21:20,245 --> 00:21:24,705
<i>I feel the wind that blows</i>
<i>towards tomorrow</i>

244
00:21:24,883 --> 00:21:30,321
<i>The city lights are like pieces of stars</i>

245
00:21:30,822 --> 00:21:35,122
<i>That hold us together</i>

246
00:21:35,594 --> 00:21:44,832
<i>"Each one of us glows differently,"</i>

247
00:21:44,903 --> 00:21:47,497
<i>you say laughingly</i>

248
00:21:47,739 --> 00:21:53,405
<i>but you look most dazzling</i>

249
00:21:53,979 --> 00:21:58,348
<i>Like a comet,</i>

250
00:21:58,417 --> 00:22:04,515
<i>like the rainbow after the storm</i>

251
00:22:04,589 --> 00:22:11,688
<i>You bring light into my heart</i>

252
00:22:12,697 --> 00:22:22,072
<i>Being lost can be the answer</i>

253
00:22:23,408 --> 00:22:30,940
<i>Let's promise we won't cheat</i>

254
00:22:31,016 --> 00:22:35,009
<i>Uh...like a shooting star,</i>
<i>we do go ahead.</i>

255
00:22:37,956 --> 00:22:40,754
Enough already, you traitor!

256
00:22:41,226 --> 00:22:44,024
Don't you dare touch
Old Lady Tsunade again!

257
00:22:44,463 --> 00:22:47,489
Hey Old Lady,
just like our wager

258
00:22:47,566 --> 00:22:50,057
I will definitely win
that unlucky necklace from you!

259
00:22:50,836 --> 00:22:53,737
I won't run away!
I won't give up!

260
00:22:54,039 --> 00:22:57,805
Just watch.
This is my Way of Ninja!

261
00:22:58,810 --> 00:23:01,836
Next time:
"Attack! Fury of the Rasengan!"
